data.name: Clackamas Middle College
data.description: I went to Clackamas Middle College, because it was a high school with dual-credit enrollment options. I would go on to graduate as a valedictorian and with an Associates Degree from Clackamas Community College
awardsList: • Graduated with an Associate of Arts Oregon Transfer Degree from Clackamas Community College

data.name: Oregon State University
data.description: I went to Oregon State University for a Bachelor's in Computer Science. Oregon State has a robust program and several extra-cirricular clubs which I have led and participated in.
awardsList: • Technology Officer of the Oregon State University Chapter of the Google Student Developer Club
• Member of the Oregon State Cybersecurity Club and the Oregon State ACM chapter
